om/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/le-sserafim-coachella-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/le-sserafim-coachella-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/k-pop">韩国流行</a>女团<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">2024 年 Coachella 音乐节上</a>首次现场表演了一首新歌 - 观看下面的表演片段。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="67" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2024-stage-set-times-line-up-how-to-watch-stream-online-3615579"><b>Coachella 2024：查看舞台时间以及如何在线直播</b></a></li></ul><p>第二天（4 月 13 日）在撒哈拉帐篷的演出期间，乐队演奏了他们的第一场 Coachella 演出，并带来了一首新曲目。这首歌的标题是“Hot And Fun”，是在“FEARLESS”、“ANTIFRAGILE”和“The Great Mermaid”等歌曲之后出现的。</p><p>乐队在副歌部分唱道：“<em>我喜欢在聚会时跳舞/我喜欢亲吻每个人</em>”。该曲目还包括半节奏的舞蹈休息。据<a href="https://m.post.naver.com/viewer/postView.naver?volumeNo=33771883&amp;memberNo=22171331" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source Music</em></a>报道，该曲目将于周一（4 月 15 日）下午 6 点（韩国时间）在流媒体上发布。</p><p>请观看下面的“Hot And Fun”片段。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">又热又有趣？？？！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f979.png" alt="🥹" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><br />简单疯狂的热 FIMCHELLA <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/LESSERAFIMatCOACHELLA?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#LESSERAFIMatCOACHELLA</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/FIMCHELLA?src=hash&amp;ref_s